<div id="c2">
<p>hi Aaron, this is a very interesting entry! you might be interested by the debates and analyses of the idea of an universal unconditional income, there are several authors discussing it but the books &#8220;Real Freedom for All&#8221; by Philippe Van Parijs, and &#8220;Redesigning Distribution&#8221; edited by Bruce Ackerman, Anne Alstott and Van Parijs (avail. for free online), are worth reading.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by pierre
 on June  9, 2008 <a href="#c2" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
